 python3,
 xinput,
 x11-xkb-utils,
 systemd
Description: Automatic keyboard layout switching for X11 based on connected keyboards
 kbd-auto-layout provides:
  - a background daemon to monitor connected keyboards
  - a CLI to manage keyboard layout rules
  - a user systemd service for automatic startup
 .
 It is intended for X11 sessions such as Xfce on Xubuntu.
